FIELD.name: Dataset
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Data set name First character indicates instrument; L=COS; I=WFC3; J=ACS; N=NICMOS; O=STIS; U=WFPC2; W=WFPC; X=FOC; Y=FOS; Z=GHRS; F=FGS; V=HSP;

FIELD.name: Target Name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Observer assigned target name; uppercase; no blank characters; spaces sometimes filled with - ; use with wildcards

FIELD.name: Ref
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The number of known literature references associated with the listed proposal ID (HST) or data set name.

FIELD.name: Apertures
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Aperture configuration See a complete list

FIELD.name: Filters/Gratings
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Filter used. See a more complete list; Sometimes combined so wildcard search may be needed

FIELD.name: Preview Name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Preview name (generally the same as the data set name)

FIELD.name: High-Level Science Products
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of known High Level Science Products
